  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nBe able to manually use a new nonce when creating transactions with `forge create` (and probably also all other transactions, could apply to cast as well).\n\n### Additional context\n\nThis is coming up because I am using `forge create` to deploy to Polygon and getting this error:\r\n`(code: -32000, message: replacement transaction underpriced, data: None)`\r\n(working in [this repo](https://github.com/R-Group-Devs/squadz-contracts))",
